    answer: "Absolutely. We check for damage, missing items, and anything that needs attention before your next guest arrives. We'll notify you immediately of any issues so you can address them or document for Airbnb claims."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you work with property managers?",
    answer: "Yes! We work with several Decatur-area property managers and offer volume pricing for multiple properties. Consistent quality, reliable scheduling, and direct communication make us a trusted partner for vacation rental management."
  },
  {
    question: "How does Wheeler Lake's seasonal demand affect Airbnb turnover scheduling?",
